## Guardian Responsibilities

### Main Guardians Should:
1. Review and approve architectural changes to the component
2. Be notified of all HLD changes affecting the component
3. Maintain component documentation and descriptor
4. Coordinate with dependent component guardians
5. Respond to questions about component capabilities

### Secondary Guardians Should:
1. Be available as backup when main guardians are unavailable
2. Stay informed about component changes
3. Assist with code reviews and implementation
4. Escalate to main guardians for major decisions

